import React, { useReducer, useState } from "react"; import "./App.css"; import { encryptString } from "./machineLogic"; import { rotors, reflector } from "./config"; import { stringify } from "querystring"; function App() { const reducer = (state: any, action: any) => { const rotate = (string: string, index: number) => string.length == 26 && string.substring(index % 26) + string.substring(0, index % 26); switch (action.type) { case "rotateRotor": return { ...state, rotors: state.rotors.map( //Iterate through rotors, shift the input and output rotor of rotor with specified index (oldValue: any, index: number) => index == action.payload.rotorIndex ? { inputRotor: rotate(oldValue.inputRow, action.payload.shift), outputRotor: rotate( oldValue.outputRow, action.payload.shift ), } : oldValue ), }; } }; const alphabet = "ABCDEFGHIJKLMNOPQRSTUVWXYZ"; const initialState = { machine: { rotors: rotors.map((rotorString: string) => { return { inputRow: rotorString, outputRow: alphabet }; }), reflector: reflector, }, input: "I am an input", }; console.log((string: string) => encryptString(string, state.machine)); const [state, dispatch] = useReducer(reducer, initialState); return (
